		<td><b>Famicom AV or Famicom with AV mod?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What's the difference of the Famicom AV(Famicom 2?) versus a Famicom with the AV mod? I wanted to get a top loader nes but I found out that it only has an RF output and if you do an AV mod on it, it will have lines thru the screen. Does the Famicom with the AV mod do the same thing as a modded top loader?
<br />
<br />Also where would be a good place to buy a famicom and a converterto play NES games on it?
<br />
<br />-Thanks!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
